tyle=3D"text-align: left;"><strong>API Developers</strong>, who are familia=
r with Mesh API development, and need to understand:</p>
<ul>
<li style=3D"text-align: left;">What is a Mesh Datastore? It's key componen=
ts, configuration, and creation &amp; deployment process</li>
<li style=3D"text-align: left;">How to consume a Mesh Datastore? Creating A=
PIs which perform CRUD operations on the datastores</li>
<li style=3D"text-align: left;">How to Deploy APIs which use the Mesh Datas=
tore? and test them out!</li>
<li style=3D"text-align: left;">Do we have a quickstart guide which can ena=
