<li><a href=3D"#Step1:CreatingadatastoreintheWestpacMesh-Step1.1:Initialise=
thedatastorerepository">Step 1.1: Initialise the datastore repository</a></=
li>
<li><a href=3D"#Step1:CreatingadatastoreintheWestpacMesh-Step1.2:CreatetheC=
QLfilestoinitialisethedatastore">Step 1.2: Create the CQL files to initiali=
se the datastore</a>
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">
<li><a href=3D"#Step1:CreatingadatastoreintheWestpacMesh-IncludingMandatory=
HeaderYellowIMPORTANT">Including Mandatory Header IMPORTANT</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Step1:CreatingadatastoreintheWestpacMesh-Modifyingtheschema=
afterDatastoreInitialization">Modifying the schema after Datastore Initiali=
zation</a>
