YellowIMPORTANT">Including Mandatory Header&nbsp;<span class=3D"status-macr=
o aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-moved">IMPORTANT</span></h3>
<p>All datastore components are required to have the Mesh Header CQL file a=
s the first change-set applied after datastore creation. The&nbsp;<span sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"><em><strong>000_mesh_header_cassandra.cql</str=
ong></em> must NEVER be changed.</span></p>
