<h3 id=3D"Step1:CreatingadatastoreintheWestpacMesh-ModifyingtheschemaafterD=
atastoreInitialization">Modifying the schema after Datastore Initialization=
</h3>
<p>Modifying previously created change-sets will result in an error since C=
assandra applies the change-sets in order, and stores the change-set hash i=
nternally.</p>
<p>If developers want to modify a schema, the changes may be included in su=
bsequent numbered files inside the change-sets folder.</p>
<h4 id=3D"Step1:CreatingadatastoreintheWestpacMesh-Example">Example</h4>
