<h3 id=3D"Step2:ConsumingtheDatastore-UseMeshHeaderHelperlibrarytopopulateM=
eshHeaderforinsert/updates"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);">Use Mesh =
Header Helper library to populate Mesh Header for insert/updates</span></h3=
>
<p>Since Mesh Header is declared as user defined type in Cassandra, a libra=
ry has been created to assist the developers in populating the fields and p=
ersisting it in their datastore with every insert/update. The attached docu=
mentation covers its usage.</p>
<p><!--
  ~ Copyright (c) 2014 by Mibex Software GmbH, Zurich, Switzerland.
  ~
  ~ All rights reserved.
  ~
  ~ This product is the proprietary and sole property of Mibex Software Gmb=
H.
