  --></p>
<div class=3D"file-macro-container include4confluence include4confluence-co=
ntent">
<div class=3D"include4confluence-panel panel" id=3D"include4confluence-bord=
er">
<div class=3D"">
<div class=3D"include4confluence-header">
<a href=3D"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projects/WDPCOM/repos/lib-m=
esh-platform-cassandra" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer">WDPCOM / lib-m=
esh-platform-cassandra /</a> <b> <a href=3D"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.c=
om.au/projects/WDPCOM/repos/lib-mesh-platform-cassandra/browse/README.md?at=
=3Drefs/heads/master" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer">README.md</a> </=
b>
<div class=3D"include4confluence-no-wrap include4confluence-meta-branch-tag=
-info">
